---
// Hero Component — Optimized
---

<section class="relative pt-16 pb-20 lg:pt-24 lg:pb-32 overflow-hidden px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12 lg:gap-20">
    
    <!-- Text Content -->
    <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center lg:items-start text-center lg:text-left z-10">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-brand font-bold text-choco leading-tight mb-6 reveal-up">
        El dulce arte de hornear felicidad. ✨
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-choco/80 font-body mb-8 max-w-2xl reveal-up delay-100">
        Descubre nuestros lienzos de sabor: pasteles y galletas diseñados con pasión como verdaderas obras de arte para Reynosa.
      </p>
      <a href="/menu" class="bg-cta text-white font-bold text-lg px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-[#D62828] active:scale-95 transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl inline-block reveal-up delay-200">
        Ver el menú completo
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 relative z-10 flex justify-center mt-10 lg:mt-0 reveal-fade delay-300">
      <div class="relative w-full max-w-md aspect-square rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-4 border-white bg-cream">
        <img 
          src="/images/pastel de fresa.jpg" 
          alt="Pastel de Fresa decorado, postre estrella de PastelArte" 
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          width="500"
          height="500"
        />
        
        <!-- Sparkle Animation -->
        <div class="sparkle-container absolute -bottom-8 -right-8 w-24 h-24 z-20 cursor-pointer" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-full h-full fill-cta drop-shadow-lg">
            <use href="#sparkle" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Decorative Elements -->
      <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-24 h-24 bg-accent/30 rounded-full blur-2xl z-0" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -left-10 w-32 h-32 bg-cta/20 rounded-full blur-2xl z-0" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
    <style>
    .sparkle-container {
      animation: float-sparkle 4s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
      transform-origin: center;
      will-change: transform;
    }
    
    @keyframes float-sparkle {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg) scale(1);
      }
      50% {
        transform: translate(-1rem, -1rem) rotate(15deg) scale(1.1);
      }
    }
  </style>
</section>
